<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>DAWTNAK CHUNGAH UM CH482</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Maw sung bik van fimnak nih leicung fimnak a lonh, Pathian dawtnak cu
 Jesuh ah tling tein a lang.

[C1]
   Hngalh in kan zumh, (Hngalh in kan zumh)2 lawm in kan hmuh, (Lawm in
   kan hmuh)2 Khuaruahhar, (Khuaruah har bia), khuaruahhar bia, (khuaruahhar
   bia, khuaruahhar, khuaruahhar bia) Pathian dawtnak chung umnak cu
   (dawtnak chung um, dawtnak chung um) Thisen thianhnak in kan hmuh
   (thianhnak in kan hmuh, in ka hmu).

[V2]
 Pathian nih a fimnak cu Baibal in a langhter, Pathian nih a thuhmi cu
 Fapa in a run phuan,

[C2]
   Hngalh in kan zumh, (Hngalh in kan zumh)2 lawm in kan hmuh, (Lawm in
   kan hmuh)2 Khuaruahhar, (Khuaruah har bia), khuaruahhar bia, (khuaruahhar
   bia, khuaruahhar, khuaruahhar bia) Pathian dawtnak chung umnak cu
   (dawtnak chung um, dawtnak chung um) Thisen thianhnak in kan hmuh
   (thianhnak in kan hmuh, in ka hmu).

[V3]
 Pathian a kan dawtnak cu zumhnak in kan hmuh cang, Kan sualnak a kan
 ngaihthiam Kal-va-ri tlang cung in,

[C3]
   Hngalh in kan zumh, (Hngalh in kan zumh)2 lawm in kan hmuh, (Lawm in
   kan hmuh)2 Khuaruahhar, (Khuaruah har bia), khuaruahhar bia, (khuaruahhar
   bia, khuaruahhar, khuaruahhar bia) Pathian dawtnak chung umnak cu
   (dawtnak chung um, dawtnak chung um) Thisen thianhnak in kan hmuh
   (thianhnak in kan hmuh, in ka hmu).

[V4]
 Thlarau kan chungah a um, Hngaltu tha bik a si, Pathian nih Khrih
 sinin langhter mi vel kong thanh u.

[C4]
   Hngalh in kan zumh, (Hngalh in kan zumh)2 lawm in kan hmuh, (Lawm in
